								</div>
								<hr style="background:#0088CC;margin:10px;margin-top:15px;">
								<div style="width:100%;padding-left:20px;" class="row">
									<div class="span3">
										<span style="display:block;margin-bottom:5px;" class="text-info">Select a prediction model:</span>
